metadata.description:
## Welcome to The first NFT Magazine to be read and collected on Ethereum!

**With this NFT Cover, you can access the exclusive **[READERS CLUB](https://www.thenftmag.io/about)** to read the content of The NFT Magazine plus the exclusive digital [Crypto Art Monograph](https://www.thenftmag.io/05-ellen-sheidlin/) of this month.**

**Also, you will be involved in decisions on the topics to be included, rankings, interviews, cover, and more of THE NFT MAGAZINE and participate to the [**"Readers Gallery" Drops**](https://www.thenftmag.io/readersgallery/) here on Nifty!**
